WEBVTT

00:02:59.600 --> 00:03:02.936
I had a childhood

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:06.680
that I would wish for anyone.

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:10.400
But when I was six,

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:17.016
the adults in my family
began to speak in whispers

00:03:17.040 --> 00:03:20.880
and shushed me any time
that I asked a question.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.256
One night,

00:03:24.280 --> 00:03:25.960
my mom and dad came.

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:29.920
They had this strange look
when they woke us.